2.3.9.2 and All in One SEO Pack Pro version 2.4.9.2. This version includes new features, bug fixes, increased security, and tons of under the hood performance improvements, including:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Confirmed 100% PHP 7 compatibility</li>\n<li>Universal Google Analytics is now used by default</li>\n<li>New API filter hook to continue to use <a href="http://semperplugins.com/documentation/use-classic-asynchronous-google-analytics-for-all-in-one-seo-pack/">classic asynchronous Google Analytics</a></li>\n<li>New API filter hook to use different <a href="http://semperplugins.com/documentation/opengraph-image-size/">featured image sizes for Open Graph social sharing</a></li>\n<li>New API filter hook to use different <a href="http://semperplugins.com/documentation/opengraph_attachment_size/">attachment image sizes for Open Graph social sharing</a></li>\n<li>Optimizations for Google Analytics codebase</li>\n<li>Fix for Edit SEO shortcut link in the Admin bar when using a dynamic homepage</li>\n<li>Improved Schema.org validation</li>\n<li>Fix for capitalization of category titles</li>\n<li>Various other under the hood improvements to the codebase</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Update your sites today to take advantage of these enhancements, improvements and bug fixes. Go to Plugins in your WordPress admin area to update.</p>\n<p><span style="font-style: italic;">Do you want access to exclusive video content, premium support, and even more features? Upgrade to <a href="http://semperplugins.com/all-in-one-seo-pack-pro-version/?loc=post2392">All in One SEO Pack Pro</a> version. Use coupon code <span style="font-weight: bold;">SUMMER2016</span> for $20.</span></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:59:"https://semperplugins.com/all-in-one-seo-pack-2-3-9-2/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"